1. Installing avocado with pip.
 pip install --user avocado-framework
2. installing pluging using pip
   pip install avocado-framework-plugin-vt avocado-framework-plugin-result-upload avocado-framework-plugin-varianter-pict avocado-framework-plugin-loader-yaml avocado-framework-plugin-resultsdb avocado-framework-plugin-runner-remote avocado-framework-plugin-robot avocado-framework-plugin-runner-vm avocado-framework-plugin-runner-docker avocado-framework-plugin-result-html
3. listing avocado tests
   avocado list

4. Listing plugins info avocado
   avocado plugins.

